flowchart TD
    REG[Validated registry contract]
    SRC[Declared source fingerprints]
    CFG[Configuration fingerprint]
    REN[Renderer identifier / interface / semantic version]
    TGT[Current target and partition fingerprints]
    SEM[Target semantics]
    ACC[Acceptance state]
    GSET[Required gate-set identity]
    BASE[Base / ref context]

    EVAL[Lifecycle-owned freshness evaluation]
    FIND[Structured independent findings]
    TRUST[Trust-state assignment]
    GATE{Existing gate authority}

    PASS[pass]
    WARN[warn]
    BLOCK[block]
    ERROR[error / fail closed]
    ACCEPT[Record acceptance state and become accepted]
    PRESERVE[Preserve bytes and prior state]
    ABANDON[Abandon attempt]

    REG --> EVAL
    SRC --> EVAL
    CFG --> EVAL
    REN --> EVAL
    TGT --> EVAL
    SEM --> EVAL
    ACC --> EVAL
    GSET --> EVAL
    BASE --> EVAL

    EVAL --> FIND
    EVAL --> TRUST
    FIND --> GATE
    TRUST --> GATE

    GATE -->|all mandatory checks pass| PASS
    GATE -->|only staged non-blocking findings| WARN
    GATE -->|freshness or safety failure| BLOCK
    GATE -->|evaluation unavailable or broken| ERROR

    PASS --> ACCEPT
    WARN --> PRESERVE
    BLOCK --> PRESERVE
    BLOCK --> ABANDON
    ERROR --> PRESERVE
    ERROR --> ABANDON

    NOTE[Renderer never assigns findings, trust state, gate outcome or acceptance]
    NOTE -. authority boundary .-> EVAL
